    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1GridLayoutParams" kindref="compound">GridLayoutParams</ref> stores per-child layout parameters for <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1GridLayout" kindref="compound">GridLayout</ref>. </para>
